<subSubSection id="C37416F0F454FFA9FF656EA358E1F792" pageId="11" pageNumber="138" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BD1457BF454FFA9FF656EA358E1F792" blockId="11.[136,1452,1315,2064]" pageId="11" pageNumber="138">
<emphasis id="B91A9969F454FFA9FF656EA35A69F83E" bold="true" box="[189,318,1927,1953]" pageId="11" pageNumber="138">Comments</emphasis>
:—The size of the urediniospores is rather variable according to data in diverse publications (
<bibRefCitation id="EFFF388AF454FFA9FAB66EA35B94F85A" author="Eboh, D. O." pageId="11" pageNumber="138" pagination="577 - 586" refId="ref11551" refString="Eboh, D. O. (1986) Taxonomic survey of Nigerian rust fungi: Uredinales Nigerianensis-IV. Mycologia 78: 577 - 586. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00275514.1986.12025292" type="journal article" year="1986">Eboh 1986</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFF388AF454FFA9FF156E885AF4F859" author="Hennen, J. F. &amp; Figueiredo, M. B. &amp; de Carvalho, Jr. A. A. &amp; Hennen, P. G." box="[205,419,1963,1990]" pageId="11" pageNumber="138" refId="ref11810" refString="Hennen, J. F., Figueiredo, M. B., de Carvalho, Jr. A. A. &amp; Hennen, P. G. (2005) Catalogue of the species of plant rust fungi (Uredinales) of Brazil. Instituto de Pesquisas, Jardim Botanico do Rio de Janeiro: Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, 490 pp." type="book" year="2005">
Hennen 
<emphasis id="B91A9969F454FFA9FEF26E885A0CF85A" box="[298,347,1963,1989]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="138">et al</emphasis>
. 2005
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFF388AF454FFA9FE756E8F5984F859" author="Cedas de Jesus, M. &amp; Mir-Leyva, S. G. &amp; Baez-Solano, A. R. &amp; Tapia-Camacho, M." box="[429,723,1963,1990]" pageId="11" pageNumber="138" pagination="2" refId="ref10780" refString="Cedas de Jesus, M., Mir-Leyva, S. G., Baez-Solano, A. R. &amp; Tapia-Camacho, M. (2018) Occurrence of rust disease caused by Puccinia thaliae on Canna indica in Mexico. SciFed Journal of Mycology 1: 2." type="journal article" year="2018">
Cedas de Jesus 
<emphasis id="B91A9969F454FFA9FD816E8859DEF85A" box="[601,649,1963,1989]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="138">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
). The size of the urediniospores of the present specimen is similar to sizes reported by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFF388AF454FFA9FEB76EEB5991F875" author="Padamsee, M. &amp; McKenzie, E. H. C." box="[367,710,1999,2026]" pageId="11" pageNumber="138" pagination="139 - 141" refId="ref13056" refString="Padamsee, M. &amp; McKenzie, E. H. C. (2012) First report of Puccinia thaliae on canna lily in New Zealand and in some Pacific island countries. Australasian Plant Disease Notes 7: 139 - 141. https: // dx. doi. org / 10.1007 / s 13314 - 012 - 0069 - 3" type="journal article" year="2012">Padamsee &amp; McKenzie [2012</bibRefCitation>
; (23–)26–36(–43) × 17–23(–27) μm] and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFF388AF454FFA9FB7C6EEB5E16F875" author="Nelson, S." box="[1188,1345,1999,2026]" pageId="11" pageNumber="138" pagination="1 - 4" refId="ref12863" refString="Nelson, S. (2013) Rust on Canna lily. Plant Disease 96: 1 - 4." type="journal article" year="2013">Nelson [2013</bibRefCitation>
; 28–40 × 20–25 μm]. 
<taxonomicName id="4C6E3EF8F454FFA9FEC96ED05A9DF792" box="[273,458,2035,2061]" class="Pucciniomycetes" family="Pucciniaceae" genus="Puccinia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Pucciniales" pageId="11" pageNumber="138" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="thaliae">
<emphasis id="B91A9969F454FFA9FEC96ED05A9DF792" box="[273,458,2035,2061]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="138">Puccinia thaliae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is reported here for the first time for 
<collectingCountry id="F37905EBF454FFA9FCB36ED758E5F792" box="[875,946,2035,2061]" name="Benin" pageId="11" pageNumber="138">Benin</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
